    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i just landed in dubai after like 14 hours on a plane and my chest kinda hurts if i breathe in deep and i feel super out of breath. i've been so stressed about this trip... do u think i'm just having a panic attack or something? it's probably just the travel anxiety right?",
